00:10:22.159 --> 00:10:26.239
think of ourselves as the sort of people who'd be taken in by something like looking for head

00:10:26.239 --> 00:10:30.400
and shoulders patterns in price charts, and certainly we don't want to think of ourselves

00:10:30.400 --> 00:10:34.880
as the sort of people who are inflicting some version of this sort of thing on our audiences.

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:39.119
For one thing, you might say, look, I'm not trying to predict the future. I just want to describe

